
These three files are used with the /proc/brightness interface provided by EC
module to control the brightness of YeeLoong via kpowersave or the other
relative applications.

install:

$ make install

or copy them manually:

$ cp preferences.fdi /etc/hal/fdi/policy
$ cp hal-system-lcd-get-brightness-linux /usr/lib/hal/scripts/linux
$ cp hal-system-lcd-set-brightness-linux /usr/lib/hal/scripts/linux
$ /etc/init.d/hal restart

NOTE:

after installing this new configuration file, you need to restart the HAL
daemon.
